*Info: If you disable Teredo, some XBOX gaming features and Windows Update Delivery Optimization will not work.*

Go to
HKEY_LOCAL_MACHINE\SOFTWARE\Policies\Microsoft\Windows\TCPIP\v6Transition
and change REG_SZ string
Teredo_State
to
Disabled

&

From an elevated command prompt, run:
netsh interface teredo set state disabled

Finish.
